Package wahoot.db.models

Class User

java.lang.Object
wahoot.db.models.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Administrator, Student, Teacher
@Entity(name="User") public abstract class User extends Object
Abstract base class for all user entities within the application. This class is mapped to the "User" table in the database and provides common attributes like username, password, email, etc.,
